    "created_at": "2017-06-12T11:44:19Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-06-12T11:44:19Z",
    "body": "While this would be a very nice feature to have, I'm afraid the ability provided by Chromium does not allow us to implement it. To be able to add this feature, we have to refactor a large part of Chromium's drag-drop code, which simply requires too much resources from us (it might take months).\r\n\r\nClosing this as won't fix"
